room_title: Escape room "Soviet Spy Game" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
room_description: Once renowned spies, you and your comrades have been brainwashed and have no memory of your identities or any intel you may have collected on behalf of your respective governments. Now on your way to the final stages of Russian Assimilation, you must find your true identities and escape before the KGB gets back to finish the job!
